Import Data from CSV Source 7

1. Open the zip file (Use the red icon above) and extract all the files, select the  .csv file for lending club loan.

2. Save it at a location in your computer.

3. Open the Power BI desktop, go to get data and select test/csv as the data source.
4. In the pop up page, browse to the location of the file.
5. Select the filename.
 6. At the bottom right side of the screen, select transformation and the data will be loaded to the query editor.


Find out more about how to connect to different data sources from

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/modules/clean-data-power-bi/
